      "description": "Exceptionally clean mint-condition car that shows extremely well inside and out. The paint, body, and interior all present beautifully with minimal to no noticeable wear, and it drives the way a properly cared-for vehicle should. Everything about it suggests careful ownership and consistent upkeep rather than a car that has been used hard. Buyers can expect a standout example that feels far above average for its age and should appeal to anyone looking for a very sharp, well-kept vehicle.",
