      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with solid everyday potential. This vehicle is best suited for a value-minded buyer looking for a practical project, spare car, or budget commuter. Priced to reflect its condition while still offering a cost-effective way to get behind the wheel, it presents a great opportunity for someone who appreciates honest value.",
