      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy spare, or a project to tinker with. It has honest wear consistent with age and use, and it\u2019s priced to reflect that while still offering real value for the right buyer. If you want something cheap, usable, and sold by someone who believes in being upfront, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
